Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:55.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}活著的事物也是無法推測的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今 Magic∞world exciting! exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此刻  Magic∞world exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.83,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}time are based on no limit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:07.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かを守れる力が欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:07.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想得到守護一個人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:14.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}からまった運命も変えていけるから
